𝙄𝙢𝙖𝙜𝙞𝙣𝙚 𝙉𝙊𝙏 𝙛𝙚𝙖𝙧𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙖 𝙗𝙞𝙠𝙞𝙣𝙞 👙 ✖
.
.
𝐈𝐦𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐧𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐟𝐫𝐞𝐞𝐝𝐨𝐦 𝐨𝐟 𝐛𝐞𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐡𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐲 𝐢𝐧 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐛𝐨𝐝𝐲 𝐧𝐨 𝐌𝐀𝐓𝐓𝐄𝐑 𝐖𝐇𝐄𝐍 🙋‍♀️
.
.
𝙄𝙢𝙖𝙜𝙞𝙣𝙚 𝙉𝙊𝙏 𝙙𝙞𝙚𝙩𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙗𝙚𝙛𝙤𝙧𝙚 𝙀𝙑𝙀𝙍𝙔 𝙝𝙤𝙡𝙞𝙙𝙖𝙮 🍔🥦
.
.
It is GENUINELY THE MOST EMPOWERING FEELING ❤ 😍
.
.
OK, I know what you're going to say back.....
.
.
That's easy for you to say. 
'Sure you've nothing to feel embarrassed about' (not my words - obviously)
.
.
Would you believe all of the above actually have VERY little to do with how actually look to other people and 100 percent have to do with how you feel about yourself on the inside 🙏
.
.
𝙸 𝚑𝚊𝚟𝚎 𝚋𝚎𝚎𝚗 𝚠𝚊𝚢 𝚕𝚎𝚊𝚗𝚎𝚛.
That does not mean I was happier. 
.
.

𝐌𝐲 𝐛𝐨𝐝𝐲 𝐢𝐬 𝐚 𝐛𝐢 𝐩𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐦𝐲 𝐥𝐢𝐟𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐲𝐥𝐞. 
I eat very well. I train regularly. And I generally look after my body. When Summer comes I'll probably gain a little extra body fat as my social life ramps up. 
.
.
But honestly, I don't view my body how most people view there's. I don't view it for what it looks like. I view it for what it can do. 
.
.
𝐁𝐞𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐁𝐢𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐑𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐲 𝐢𝐬 𝐍𝐎𝐓 𝐚 𝐥𝐨𝐨𝐤 𝐛𝐮𝐭 𝐚 𝐟𝐞𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐠 ❤
.
.
If you want that feeling why not join my Girl gang? Summer is just around the corner and I want everyone to feel this way in a bikini 👙🙏
.
.

28 Day Kickstarter 

‼️I'm looking for 5 ladies who want to become strong and confident while eating the foods they enjoy‼️
.
.
Feel like you've tried everything and still see no results? Here's 3 reasons my coaching programme could work for you: 

1. I educate women on nutrition. I don't give meal plans but actually teach you the importance of nutrient dense food. I help you calculate calories and understand the foods you need to fuel your body. I'm also a big advocate of including foods you actually enjoy! 

2. Want to be able to lift your suitcase with ease when lockdown finishes? Want to perform a push up? Want to become a strong, independent female?
I focus on resistance training and encourage women to become the strongest they can be. 

3. I help women become the best versions of themselves. Confidence comes from the inside out and I help women find that sassy female that's hiding inside. 

I know sometimes people are afraid to make a long term commitment so this kickstarter may be exactly what you need to start your health and fitness journey with me. Did I also mention the incredible community that comes with it? 

When does it start?
Monday 6th September. 

Applications close: 
Friday 3rd 

If you're ready to become the strongest, most confident version of yourself - Dm Me 'Kickstart' to hear more.

Who wants to make changes like this 👇👇👇

Aoibheann's Experience:
.
.
I started the programme as I wanted to lose some weight- I decided that 2021 was my year. And found Amanda on Instagram. Working with Amanda I have unreal encouragement and constant support. 
.
.
If anyone had told me I’d feel this way after just 12 weeks I wouldn’t believe them.. in fact when I started this in January I didn’t really think much would change.. But everything from my mindset to my confidence to my understanding of food and realising how great my body is, the importance of listening to your body and what I need to fuel it. 
.
.
I no longer feel guilty for having treats at the weekend or having a few drinks because that’s just a small part of my life. Staying consistent is key. 
.
.
I don’t think I’ve ever heard of a Coach who cares as much for there clients mental well-being as much as Amanda does. Feeling extremely grateful for you and all the girls, it’s so nice to share this journey in a community of such likeminded people ❤️
.
.
And 14 weeks on she's still on her journey 🙏
P.s Look at that smile 🥰
